reviews: I saw this film at the London Film Festival, and it was a breath of fresh air. Unpretentious, and very funny. I'm surprised the lead actor isn't working all the time. The women are sexy. And the view of New York society from the working class point of view seems right on. I want more!
summaries: A dark comedy about the wild night Hank has when he discovers that he has won a $200 million lottery jackpot.
